description	"Zuckuss

Class: Arc Trooper.
Class Summary: 
A speedy dexterous gunner/melee hybrid with permanent radar sense and a powerful limited-ammo gun. 

Weaponry:
- W-90 Concussion Rifle (Based on T21 Level 1 with enhanced knockback and rate of fire)
- Gand Shock Staff *

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- Gand Shock Staff
- Defense (1)
- Can use Staff and Yellow styles
- Reduced damage compared to Saber
- Can block lightsabers
- Can block blaster shots

Attributes:
- Heal (2)
- Shield Recharge (1)

Abilities:
- Stamina (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dodge (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dexterity (3) [Alt Ability 1]

Force abilities:
- Mind Trick Immunity
- Findsman Precognition (Permanent Sense level 1)

An infamous bounty hunter and Gand Findsman with uncanny tracking abilities that could be considered a sixth sense. He often took bounties alongside 4-LOM."